    "title": "夏合宿のお知らせ",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "お疲れ様です、トレーナーさん！\r\n日々がんばっておられますね。",
            "enText": "Good job, trainer! You are\nworking hard every day.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "pathId": -9006864260046553209,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "ところで……いよいよ今年も、\r\nこの時期がやって参りましたよ！",
            "enText": "By the way… it's finally that\ntime of year again!",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "pathId": 4603767581867003930,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "もうすぐトレセン学園恒例、\r\n『夏合宿』期間の到来です～！",
            "enText": "It's almost time for the annual\n\"Summer Camp\" at Tracen Academy!",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "夏合宿……！",
                    "enText": "Summer Camp…!",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                }
            ],
            "coloredText": [
                {
                    "jpText": "夏合宿",
                    "enText": "Summer Camp"
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4760954736590749584,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "はいっ♪　施設に泊まり込みで行う、\r\nいつもと一風変わったトレーニング……。",
            "enText": "This is a different kind of training, where\nyou stay overnight at the facility…",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "coloredText": [
                {
                    "jpText": "一風変わったトレーニング",
                    "enText": "a different kind of training"
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7960651010871117290,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "きっと担当ウマ娘も、\r\nいつもより大きく成長できると思います！",
            "enText": "I'm sure your horse girl will\ngrow even more than usual!",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "coloredText": [
                {
                    "jpText": "大きく成長できる",
                    "enText": "grow even more"
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8721812831839180494,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "……なので、夏合宿の始まる『7月』に向け、\r\n体調を万全に整えてあげてくださいね。",
            "enText": "… So please make sure she's in good shape\nfor the summer camp in July.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "coloredText": [
                {
                    "jpText": "7月",
                    "enText": "July"
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "体調を万全",
                    "enText": "in good shape"
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6392270416410941665,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "夏合宿はあっという間！\r\n『お休み』してるヒマなんてありませんから。",
            "enText": "Summer camp goes by so fast! There's\nno time to take a \"break\".",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "わかりました！",
                    "enText": "Yes, ma'am!",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5070574368289057306,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "いいお返事です！\r\nふふっ、楽しみですね～夏合宿♪",
            "enText": "Good reply! Hehe… I'm looking\nforward to it… Summer camp ♪",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "pathId": 3913479963152858373,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "そうそう、練習第一であることは\r\nもちろんなのですが……。",
            "enText": "Yes, of course, practice comes first, but…",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "pathId": -3173677212346404099,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "たまには息抜きに、海へ『お出かけ』！\r\nというのもいいかもしれませんね♪",
            "enText": "Sometimes it's nice to take a break\nand \"go out\" to the beach!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "pathId": 4580535460047245747,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "担当ウマ娘もリフレッシュできて、\r\n疲れも取れると思いますよ～！",
            "enText": "I'm sure it will refresh your horse\ngirl and relieve her fatigue!",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "なるほど……",
                    "enText": "I see…",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4274997313484872894,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "7月から8月までの『2か月』という、\r\n短い時間ではありますが――",
            "enText": "It's only a short two months\nfrom July to August, but…",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "coloredText": [
                {
                    "jpText": "7月から8月までの『2か月』",
                    "enText": "from July to August"
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6328090065851614697,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "駿川たづな",
            "enName": "Hayakawa Tazuna",
            "jpText": "実り多き『夏合宿』を、\r\n担当ウマ娘と共にお過ごしください♪",
            "enText": "Please spend a fruitful \"summer\ncamp\" with your horse girl.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "pathId": -3969968202761452241,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "たづなさんから\r\n『夏合宿』についての話を聞いた！",
            "enText": "Tazuna told me about the \"summer camp\"!",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "pathId": 3853869183264115067,
            "blockIdx": 14
